subject: ¡Tu futuro te está esperando! Actualiza tu CV hoy mismo.
body:
VIEW MESSAGE IN BROWSER

Hola Julio Cesar,

¡Gracias por ser parte de nuestra comunidad! Sabemos que tu tiempo es valioso y que, como profesional, siempre buscas nuevas oportunidades para crecer y avanzar en tu carrera. Para asegurarnos de que tu perfil sea el primero en destacarse ante las empresas, te invitamos a que actualices tu CV con la información más reciente.

Razones por las que debes actualizar tu CV ahora:

 - Más visibilidad para ti:  Las empresas buscan profesionales con habilidades y experiencia actualizada. Mantener tu perfil actualizado aumenta las posibilidades de ser contactado.
 - Oportunidades personalizadas:  Al tener un CV actualizado, las ofertas de empleo que recibas estarán alineadas con tus habilidades actuales y lo que realmente estás buscando.
 - El primer paso para nuevos retos:  Un CV actualizado refleja tu crecimiento profesional y te posiciona como un candidato más competitivo.

Es rápido y fácil. ¡No pierdas la oportunidad de ser considerado para las mejores ofertas laborales!

subject: Join our livestream on July 10th and celebrate 35 years of defending digital rights
body:
EFFECTING CHANGE LIVESTREAM SERIES 
Hi ​Customer​,

Join us on Thursday, July 10 at 11:00 AM for a special 35th anniversary edition of the EFFecting Change Livestream Series: EFF Turns 35! EFF's lawyers, activists, analysts, and technologists have used everything in their toolkit to defend your freedom online. Over the last 35 years, they've seen it all. Now learn what's next for your digital rights. 

EFFecting Change Livestream Series: 
EFF Turns 35! 
Thursday, July 10 11:00 AM - 12:00 PM Pacific
Check Local Time: https://dateful.com/eventlink/1636667650
RSVP TODAY: www.eff.org/livestream-35

Join our panel featuring EFF Executive Director Cindy Cohn, EFF Legislative Director Lee Tien, EFF Director of Cybersecurity Eva Galperin, and Professor/EFF Board Member Yoshi Kohno for a discussion exploring what's next for technology users.

We encourage you to join us live for this discussion, however it will be recorded and available following the event on YouTube (www.eff.org/EFfectingChangeRecordings) and the Internet Archive (www.eff.org/EFFectingChangeArchive)! If you already have some questions for the panelists, feel free to reply here and we'll add it to our list. 

See you there, 

Melissa Srago 
EFF Membership Team 

P.S. Throughout 2025, EFF staff will host experts in their field that will dive into topics that are sure to spur questions and a desire for change. Check out www.eff.org/EFFectingChange for the lineup! Want to make sure you don’t miss an announcement? Sign up for updates about this series at www.eff.org/ECUpdates. 

EFF is dedicated to a harassment-free experience for everyone, and all participants are encouraged to view our full Event Expectations: www.eff.org/pages/event-expectations.

Thank you to Fastly and DuckDuckGo for their year-round support of EFF's mission. Please visit www.eff.org/thanks or contact tierney@eff.org for more information on corporate giving and sponsorships.

This message is printed from 100% recycled electrons. EFF appreciates your support and respects your privacy: www.eff.org/policy.

subject: Today is EFF’s 35th anniversary and we’re just getting started
body:
35 YEARS FOR INTERNET FREEDOM
---

Hi  Digital Rights Supporter ,

Today we celebrate 35 years of EFF bearing the torch for digital rights against the darkness of the world, and I couldn’t be prouder.

EFF was founded at a time when governments were hostile toward technology and clueless about how it would shape your life. While threats from state and commercial forces grew alongside the internet, so too did EFF’s expertise.

Our mission has become even larger than pushing back on government ignorance and increasingly dangerous corporate power. In this moment, we're doing our part to preserve the necessities of democracy: privacy, free expression, and due process. It's about guarding the security of our society, along with our loved ones and the vulnerable communities around us.

With the support of EFF’s members, we use law, technology, and activism to create the conditions for human rights and civil liberties to flourish, and for repression to fail.

EFF believes in commonsense freedom and fairness. We’re working toward an environment where your technology works the way you want it to; you can move through the world without the threat of surveillance; and you can have private conversations with the people you care about and support the causes you believe in. We’ve won many fights for encryption, free expression, innovation, and your personal data throughout the years. The opposition is tough, but—with a powerful vision for a better future and you on our side—EFF is formidable.

Throughout EFF’s year-long 35th Anniversary celebration, our dedicated activists, investigators, technologists, and attorneys will share the lessons from EFF’s long and rich history so that we can help overcome the obstacles ahead.

TOGETHER FOR THE DIGITAL FUTURE

As a member-supported nonprofit, everything EFF does depends on you. Donate to help fuel the fight for privacy, free expression, and a future where we protect digital freedom for everyone.

Join EFF: https://eff.org/r.cus9

Powerful forces may try to chip away at your rights—but when we stand together, we win.

WATCH TODAY: EFFECTING CHANGE LIVE

Just hours from now, join me for the 35th Anniversary edition of our EFFecting Change livestream: https://www.eff.org/event/effecting-change-eff-turns-35.

I’m leading this Q&A with EFF Director for International Freedom of Expression Jillian York, EFF Legislative Director Lee Tien, and Professor and EFF Board Member Yoshi Kohno. Together, we’ve seen it all and today we hope you'll join us for what’s next.

WATCH LIVE: https://eff.org/livestream
TIME: 11:00 AM Pacific. Check your local time at https://dateful.com/eventlink/1636667650

EFF supporters around the world sustain our mission to defend technology creators and users. Thank you for being a part of this community and helping it thrive.

For your freedom online,

Cindy Cohn
EFF Executive Director

P.S. We’re celebrating TWELVE YEARS of top ratings from the nonprofit watchdog Charity Navigator! EFF is a member-supported U.S. 501(c)(3) and your donation is tax-deductible as allowed by law.

---

About EFF
The Electronic Frontier Foundation is the leading nonprofit defending online civil liberties. We promote digital innovation, defend free speech, fight illegal surveillance, and protect rights and freedoms for all as our use of technology grows. Find out more at https://www.eff.org./

body:
Shape the future of Prezi

Hi Julio,

Thank you for using Prezi!

We’d like to invite you to participate in a short questionnaire ➡️ https://ablink.create.prezi.com/ls/click?upn=u001.MF8fF5TsPypvZJ64A5B3hoOu6wmSC-2F40ZXmg0-2FC30AuMoPcMq599g44QuhQOSm8dnAJsugoJag1qc3LmMZAMp1sLAxc6QV-2BluFy3DsSzq77YPruiwIkyxQcofHSMpLyChfn2_0JGemXNmYQk34HgfYGxranYPOe286hgISbr79CfD5m01vJCZ-2FwnRzLSnOBZ9KBaGhWwYhV4FvDvWciQYsMVfy7a4LXUIsGLECSBAU9mwf4wNt7FErIsurFee4EkCxF0aVGbKEhWwY9Jld4ETJxT9stIPyO7poZjcKBhjih-2B2HCgWkNO9YwZ2LrwPICBWbgdxGYRoSlrn0gO-2F49u47EA8lGvNJpqLVYe9TAZYs7JkIVcNIFaMeJj-2FctJxZ-2Bfvp5fnoLJV1VEPsxNnK7SPAAJMC2CcJ-2F321yRMlUHR3O6r8giEHno-2BW3ph-2FSbj7i6GKDoqTcbcAk-2FGGWV8Z-2Fi77gR3hQVttjV4GG8mdPoUgrKX4bT67SSAE98oK3QbGQMWCktL-2BwVf-2FnKVXrJcoFbkd-2FVRINM6l5CYG1zSHdyi1V-2B-2B0MzQ5CuXU-2BRWphXLn-2FmR3mqiWWSWE0I1Wi2qhNcy9cr9fgUsz3mTwdjyRsE2V-2F4sEbzSHHA-2FxCt3yFFN9ETrhSyNoUmx5SZZNd-2F0FksnY6SteQN695aD-2FN2S6ams0pqDQ56HSwVKkpBNvG3hOGtIqES6WzhIaxZ-2BCFwldas57b32XVSxDVOeyPtfqQXFkEwCu5qjybUGw7b9ux55fOLXjbOQ5938XN8z9XUc7twNQSG6Tw-3D-3D to better understand your experience with Prezi.

RECOMENDACIONES

*TIPS ANTIFRAUDE:*

Club Sunset y Club Hacienda Tres Ríos le ofrece los siguientes tips para evitar que sea víctima de fraude:

TODA COMUNICACIÓN POR EMAIL LA ENVIAMOS DESDE LOS DOMINIOS OFICIALES DE SUNSET WORLD:

*@SUNSET.COM.MX* y *@SUNSET.MX*

Cuando reciba un email que aparentemente es de su club, verifique bien el dominio porque los defraudadores en ocasiones solo agregan o quitan una letra para confundirle.

*ES PROBABLE QUE EN ESTOS CORREOS LE OFREZCAN:*

• OFERTAS DE HOSPEDAJE A MUY BAJO COSTO

• PAQUETES VACACIONALES CON TOURS GRATIS

• PAQUETES VACACIONALES CON FECHAS ABIERTAS HASTA DE 24 MESES Y SIN RESTRICCIONES DE USO DE SEMANAS

• LA COMPRA / VENTA DE SU MEMBRESÍA

• LA RENTA DE SUS SEMANAS CORPORATIVAS Y REGULARES

• CANTIDADES QUE VAN MÁS ALLÁ DEL VALOR DE SU MEMBRESÍA, PROPORCIONÁNDOLE DOCUMENTACIÓN FALSA DE ENTIDADES DEL GOBIERNO

• LE SOLICITAN COPIA DE SU CONTRATO E IDENTIFICACIONES

• LE EXIGEN PAGOS CON TRANSFERENCIA BANCARIA, PORQUE ES LA ÚNICA FORMA DE QUE USTED NO PUEDA RECUPERAR SU DINERO

La forma más segura de realizar sus pagos es a través de los teléfonos del Corporativo de Atención a Miembros de Club Sunset o Club Hacienda Tres Ríos y en el portal de socios www.sunsetworldresorts.com ( https://www.sunsetworldresorts.com )

Por favor ponga mucha *ATENCIÓN* a la información que recibe y *NO* realice ninguna transferencia si no ha verificado la información en los números oficiales de Sunset World:

Mantente conectado

( https://www.facebook.com/SunsetWorld ) ( https://www.instagram.com/sunsetworldnet ) ( https://x.com/sunsetworldnet/ ) ( https://www.youtube.com/@SunsetworldNet )

> El jue., 25 feb. 2021 11:52 a. m., support claessonedwards.com <support@claessonedwards.com> escribió:
> Hello,
>  
> I have confirmed your order and noticed your license has already been upgraded to a BreakawayOne 1x Full FM license key. You would need a new key in order to use it on your new pc.
> We need your configuration information before we can issue your new BreakawayOne license key.
> If you have not already installed BreakawayOne, here is the download link:
> http://www.breakawayone.com/downloads/
> Install it on the system(s) where you want to register BreakawayOne. 
> Launch the BreakawayOne Config application.  Click on the Main Configuration button and then the Audio Processing Cores button and adjust the sliders to enable the audio processing cores that you require.  Then click on the Apply button.
> Next, launch the BreakawayOne App and complete the setup.  Here is some setup information:
> How to configure an audio processing core  http://www.claessonedwards.com/downloads/Basic_Config.pdf
>     Here is a YouTube video which shows how to enable and configure an HD core:  https://youtu.be/EGIIuRJI0H0
> How to configure the Streaming Encoder  http://www.claessonedwards.com/downloads/Streaming_Encoder_Setup.pdf
>        Here is a YouTube video which shows how to configure the Streaming Encoder:  https://youtu.be/t_6MKp-t56g
> During the trial period all of the BreakawayOne features are fully enabled so that you can complete your evaluation before requesting your license.
> Once you have confirmed that BreakawayOne is performing as required, launch the BreakawayOne App and select [Common] – [System] – [License Information], then press [Get License Summary].  Then copy & paste the configuration information text into the return email.
> Here is a link to a YouTube video which shows how to "Get License Summary":  https://youtu.be/jdLcBJO3hfw
> The license key will only authorize BreakawayOne to operate on the computer listed in your configuration.  You will have to contact us before attempting to move the license to another computer.  So make sure to request the license for the correct computer. 
> Your license key will be issued once we receive your configuration information. There are no refunds or recalls for any reason after the license has been issued.  So be sure that you are completely satisfied with your BreakawayOne setup before sending us the configuration information.
> Regards
> John

subject: ¡Tu futuro te está esperando! Actualiza tu CV hoy mismo.
body:
VIEW MESSAGE IN BROWSER

Hola Julio Cesar,

¡Gracias por ser parte de nuestra comunidad! Sabemos que tu tiempo es valioso y que, como profesional, siempre buscas nuevas oportunidades para crecer y avanzar en tu carrera. Para asegurarnos de que tu perfil sea el primero en destacarse ante las empresas, te invitamos a que actualices tu CV con la información más reciente.

Razones por las que debes actualizar tu CV ahora:

 - Más visibilidad para ti:  Las empresas buscan profesionales con habilidades y experiencia actualizada. Mantener tu perfil actualizado aumenta las posibilidades de ser contactado.
 - Oportunidades personalizadas:  Al tener un CV actualizado, las ofertas de empleo que recibas estarán alineadas con tus habilidades actuales y lo que realmente estás buscando.
 - El primer paso para nuevos retos:  Un CV actualizado refleja tu crecimiento profesional y te posiciona como un candidato más competitivo.

subject: New: Paste SVG & Lottie in AE ✨
body:
LF June 2025
Easily animate your creations!
Paste SVG or Lottie JSON to After Effects
You can now copy and paste SVGs or Lottie JSON as an AE composition from the Import tab. Just copy from your design tool (like Figma) or SVG files and paste them into the AE plugin.
Explore More
The next chapter of Lottie animations
The future of motion is more open, flexible, and connected than you think—and with LottieFiles, it’s just getting started. With powerful tools, deeper integrations, and a smoother workflow, we’re making motion easy for everyone.
Read More
Interactivity
dotLottie slider
Experience how dotLottie makes interactivity easy—slide through emotions and see smooth animations update instantly.
See Codepen
"When using animation in UI, remember: the more an object moves, the higher its position in the visual hierarchy."
Ken Mahakim
Visual Designer
Community
How Spoon cut animation sizes by 90% & doubled speed
Discover how Spoon cut animation file sizes and doubled release speed, and enriched gifting with dynamic, lightweight Lottie animations, turning every interaction into a moment of delight.
Read the Full Story
Hatch Conference Berlin & Online
Join our Design Engineer, Carmen, for a candid talk on why trusting your intuition, embracing high-fidelity prototyping, and staying flexible through rapid changes can help you build better products. Come hang out and learn with us!
Explore More

Greetings!

Felix

Sone G - Rescue Me
// Jamaica-Canada

Language: English
Explicit Lyrics: No

EPK: https://promo.boomrush-productions.de/?p=11829https://promo.boomrush-productions.de/?p=11829 (password: music)

File under: Gospel Reggae

- Website https://www.soneg.live
- Facebook https://www.facebook.com/sonegmusic/
- Instagram https://www.instagram.com/_sone_g
- YouTube https://www.youtube.com/soneministries


Gospel reggae artist Sone G returns with his powerful new single "Rescue Me", a heartfelt anthem that testifies to the unchanging faithfulness of God in times of trouble. Blending roots reggae rhythms with spiritual conviction, the track becomes available on all major streaming platforms on July 10, 2025.
"Rescue Me" is more than just a song — it’s a personal cry, a praise, and a reminder that no matter how many times we fall, God is always ready to reach down and pull us up. Inspired by real-life challenges and divine encounters, Sone G delivers this message with passion, vulnerability, and a deep sense of worship.
“There were times in my life where I thought that life is just overwhelming,” says Sone G. “But every single time, God showed up. That’s what this song is about — He never fails to rescue us.” […]

Claude 4 is here—and it’s your most thoughtful AI partner yet. 










Hello,



Claude 4 is here—and it’s your most thoughtful AI partner yet. 



What you can do now:

 * Get deeper insights: Ask Claude to think step-by-step through complex 
problems so you both understand the problem better
 *  Coding got better: If you already code with Claude, you'll love 
this—Claude is now the world's best AI coding assistant
 * Get creative together: Whether you’re writing or brainstorming, Claude 
feels like working with a creative friend 


Try Claude 4 now  <https://claude.ai>



Want to do even more? 



We’ve recently expanded capabilities for Pro and Max users: 

 * Access to all models: Choose between different Claude models, including the 
powerful new Claude Opus 4
 * Code in your terminal: Use Claude Code directly for terminal-based coding 
workflows
 *  Research anything: Get comprehensive answers in minutes
 * Connect your tools: Link Claude to your favorite apps and workflows 
Free users get access to Claude Sonnet 4, and you can always upgrade to unlock 
the full experience.



Explore Claude plans  <https://claude.ai/upgrade>



—The Anthropic Team




 <https://www.anthropic.com/?utm_source=email>

 <https://x.com/anthropicai>  
<https://www.linkedin.com/company/anthropicresearch> 
<https://www.youtube.com/@anthropic-ai>

subject: Keep up to date with VirusTotal features
body:
Wednesday, Aug 6, 2025






Hi Julio,



We want to continue to open your eyes to VirusTotal functionality that you might have missed.


Did you know that you can keep up to date with our latest features and changes both in our main blog and our release notes? They are great resources beyond our technical documentation.


VirusTotal Blog


Not feeling like reading? Our past webinars might be particularly appealing, and our YouTube Channel.







Feel free to contact us anytime!






Tw Inst Yt




Happy hunting!






If you are not interested in receiving more invitations for future VT communications you can clear the "Onboarding hand-holding" checkbox in your email preferences center (sign in required) or unsubscribe via email.

subject: Missed out on Team '25? Join a live webinar with Atlassian leaders to catch up!
body:
Atlassian

All the headlines from Team '25

Learn more
>> https://webinars.atlassian.com/series/team-25-announcements-leadership/series_details?utm_source=sfmc&utm_medium=email&event_context=701qb00000lg6obyar&utm_campaign=B1-EML-19123&jobid=107086898&subid=1843452558

At our Team '25 conference this month, we gathered nearly 5,000 customers, partners, and Atlassians to unveil our biggest set of announcements yet.

Our customers are hungry for solutions as they wrestle with siloed teams, ineffective communication, and information overload. That's exactly why we're redefining collaboration for teams like yours around the globe.

Take a moment to explore all the key headlines from Team '25 below. If you want to learn more, be sure to register for our webinar and live Q&A session on May 7 with Atlassian leaders, President Anu Bharadwaj and Chief Marketing Officer, Zeynep Inanoglu Ozdemir. 
>> https://webinars.atlassian.com/series/team-25-announcements-leadership/series_details?utm_source=sfmc&utm_medium=email&event_context=701qb00000lg6obyar&utm_campaign=B1-EML-19123&jobid=107086898&subid=1843452558

Rovo is now available for all customers at no extra cost

With our AI capabilities already redefining work for over a million users every month, it's clear the future of teamwork is human-AI collaboration. To bring that future closer, we're making our enterprise AI solution, Rovo, available so that all of our customers can bring the most advanced AI-powered search, chat, and agents to their teams.

Learn more
>> https://www.atlassian.com/blog/announcements/team25-rovo-for-all?utm_source=sfmc&utm_medium=email&event_context=701qb00000lg6obyar&utm_content=K%3Aevent%7CH%3Aany%7CN%3ATeam_25%7CP%3Aagnostic%7CO%3Aevent-marketing%7CF%3Apost-event%7CC%3Aevent-home&utm_campaign=B1-EML-19123&jobid=107086898&subid=1843452558

Teamwork Collection is here to reimagine how teams collaborate

Are functional silos, ineffective AI, and disconnected tools slowing your teams down? Enter Teamwork Collection: a curated selection of apps - Jira, Confluence, and Loom - and powerful Rovo agents, that will reimagine how your teams collaborate.

Learn more
>> https://www.atlassian.com/blog/announcements/teamwork-collection?utm_source=sfmc&utm_medium=email&event_context=701qb00000lg6obyar&utm_content=K%3Aevent%7CH%3Aany%7CN%3ATeam_25%7CP%3Aagnostic%7CO%3Aevent-marketing%7CF%3Apost-event%7CC%3Aevent-home&utm_campaign=B1-EML-19123&jobid=107086898&subid=1843452558

Strategy Collection will connect work, goals, and teams to company priorities

Purpose-built for leaders of technology-driven organizations, Strategy Collection is a single solution for enterprise strategy and planning. Evolve your enterprise strategy with this collection of apps - Focus, Talent, and Align - that help leaders deliver better outcomes across their businesses.

Learn more
>> https://www.atlassian.com/blog/announcements/strategy-collection?utm_source=sfmc&utm_medium=email&event_context=701qb00000lg6obyar&utm_content=K%3Aevent%7CH%3Aany%7CN%3ATeam_25%7CP%3Aagnostic%7CO%3Aevent-marketing%7CF%3Apost-event%7CC%3Aevent-home&utm_campaign=B1-EML-19123&jobid=107086898&subid=1843452558

Platform Apps will become your favorite everyday destinations

Every Atlassian Cloud app and Collection comes with pre-loaded Platform Apps, such as Goals and Home, helping you connect teams and accelerate your work.

Learn more
>> http://www.atlassian.com/platform/platform-apps?utm_source=sfmc&utm_medium=email&event_context=701qb00000lg6obyar&utm_content=K%3Aevent%7CH%3Aany%7CN%3ATeam_25%7CP%3Aagnostic%7CO%3Aevent-marketing%7CF%3Apost-event%7CC%3Aevent-home&utm_campaign=B1-EML-19123&jobid=107086898&subid=1843452558

AI in Jira Service Management will deliver exceptional service experiences

New AI capabilities in ITSM help customers deliver even better employee support and resolve incidents faster.

Learn more
>> https://www.atlassian.com/blog/announcements/jira-service-management-agentic-ai?utm_source=sfmc&utm_medium=email&event_context=701qb00000lg6obyar&utm_content=K%3Aevent%7CH%3Aany%7CN%3ATeam_25%7CP%3Aagnostic%7CO%3Aevent-marketing%7CF%3Apost-event%7CC%3Aevent-home&utm_campaign=B1-EML-19123&jobid=107086898&subid=1843452558

New Cloud deployment options are here to accelerate your journey to the cloud

To help even more organizations benefit from Atlassian Cloud, we're introducing new deployment options: Atlassian Government Cloud, in early access, and Atlassian Isolated Cloud, coming in 2026.

Learn more
>> https://www.atlassian.com/blog/announcements/expanding-pathways-to-cloud?utm_source=sfmc&utm_medium=email&event_context=701qb00000lg6obyar&utm_content=K%3Aevent%7CH%3Aany%7CN%3ATeam_25%7CP%3Aagnostic%7CO%3Aevent-marketing%7CF%3Apost-event%7CC%3Aevent-home&utm_campaign=B1-EML-19123&jobid=107086898&subid=1843452558

Top announcements from Team '25 with Atlassian Leadership

Tune in to a free, live webinar with Atlassian leaders Anu Bharadwaj and Zeynep Inanoglu Ozdemir on May 7 at 11:00 AM PDT or May 8 at 11:00 AM AEST / 11:00 AM CEST to get the rundown on everything we've announced.

Register now

subject: Action Recommended: Oracle Cloud Infrastructure SDK for Java - Early upgrade option to SDK v3 for Java  for Tenant: jcas3322 - [CN-972932]
body:
Cloud Infrastructure
Oracle Cloud Infrastructure SDK for Java - Early upgrade option to SDK v3 for Java
Oracle Cloud Infrastructure Customer,
Oracle has recently released support for Oracle Cloud Infrastructure (OCI) SDK v3 for Java (also known as version 3.0.0 for Java), and we recommend that you upgrade to the latest version.
How will this affect my service?
There will be no impact to your service. You may continue to use previous versions of the OCI SDK for Java in your environments without any impact on current functionality.
We will continue to support OCI SDK v2 for Java for a period of six months until June 13, 2023. During this six-month period, the v2 version will be supported in conjunction with the new OCI SDK v3 for Java, so that you will have sufficient time to upgrade to v3.
Post-June 13, 2023: There will still be no impact to your service, and you may continue to use previous versions of the OCI SDK for Java. However, you will no longer receive weekly updates for new services, latest features, and bug fixes in older versions including v2.
After this date, OCI SDK v2 for Java will enter maintenance mode for a period of 12 months, during which updates to this version will be limited to addressing critical bug fixes and security patching. Following this 12 month maintenance mode, updates to the OCI SDK v2 for Java will be discontinued.
Are there any actions I need to take?
Yes. We highly recommend that you upgrade to the OCI SDK v3 for Java to continue receiving weekly support for new services, latest features, and bug fixes.
Action Recommended
Action Required By:
June 13, 2023 00:00 UTC
Service(s):
Oracle Cloud Infrastructure SDK for Java
Tenant Name:
jcas3322
Where can I find additional information?
For more information about OCI SDK v3 for Java, please refer to our announcement blog: https://blogs.oracle.com/cloud-infrastructure/post/announcing-oci-java-sdk-300.
For a detailed guide on list of changes you need to make to migrate to OCI SDK v3 for Java, please see Updates in the OCI SDK for Java 3: https://docs.oracle.com/en-us/iaas/Content/API/SDKDocs/javasdk3.htm.
You can also view what’s changed in our Changelog: https://github.com/oracle/oci-java-sdk/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md.
For the getting started guide and examples, please refer to Getting Started with SDK for Java: https://docs.oracle.com/en-us/iaas/Content/API/SDKDocs/javasdkgettingstarted.htm and Examples: https://docs.oracle.com/en-us/iaas/Content/API/SDKDocs/javasdkexamples.htm.
What should I do if I am still having an issue?
Please
contact support
to create a Service Request and provide the Reference Number and Tenant ID shown below.

subject: An AI for voice cloning - is it any good?
body:
----------
Roughly 117 billion people have ever lived on Earth.

You’re one of them.

And somehow, your group chat still can't pick a dinner spot.

**What’s in store:**

* **Eleven Labs **isn’t that complicated after all.

* Our **tool of the week** is…

* Read [**30 of the hottest AI takes**](https://offers.hubspot.com/brutally-honest-ai-predications?utm_medium=email-media-newsletter&utm_source=mindstream&utm_campaign=owned&utm_term=2025-08-09&utm_content=native-ads) from industry leaders!

_Read Time: 4 minutes_


--------------------
###### **ELEVENLABS**

## I Tried Eleven Labs so You Don’t Have To

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/445972bf-5b9b-46af-8e20-bf962003fb41/u8676618187_Pixel_art_style_of_a_futuristic_voice_lab_filled__4e3f3358-7a2c-4112-91ed-bbc498477593_0.png?t=1754657967)
Follow image link: (https://www.mindstream.news/)
Caption: 

ElevenLabs is a text-to-speech (TTS) and voice cloning tool on steroids, so obviously, we had to try it. 

People use Eleven Labs for a variety of reasons, whether it’s making a podcast, creating a voiceover for a video, or creating a narration version of a written article on your website (which could be for accessibility purposes). We were a bit overwhelmed by the options! 

So, here’s how you can get started:

### **Jumping in**

First, you can sign up for the free version, and it’ll ask you a couple of questions about how you plan to use it. Honestly, we hit ‘skip’ for now. Once you’re in, click on the toggle on the left-hand side that says ‘Creative Platform’.

The dashboard was very user-friendly if you just want to get an overview of what's available. Just click ‘Home’ on the left-hand side navigation to get there.

### **Explore the insane voice library**

The first thing we noticed was the Voice Library, where ElevenLabs gives you more than 5,000 voices to choose from and then tweak to your needs. For example, the voice we picked was talking too slowly, so we sped it up!

And, get this... You can also make money by publishing your voice on ElevenLabs, too. If someone decides to use your voice for their project, you’ll earn royalties. Pretty sweet, no?

### **Try text-to-speech to hear your story come to life**

This tool lets you drop in your script, then pick a voice (if you haven’t already), and listen. Theoretically, you could use this to practice an actual speech you have to give by uploading/cloning your own voice to the platform. 

One thing: we’re used to putting a prompt or copying my text into that little space at the bottom of the page, like you would in ChatGPT, but we couldn’t figure this out right away! Instead, you copy the text in at the top , like a doc. Thank us later!

### **Get funky with sound effects**

This cool tool was kind of like the Midjourney of sounds. This could be used to add a sound effect to another project you’re working on (perhaps in the ‘Studio’ section), or just to play around with it. You’d prompt this the way you’d prompt in Claude, ChatGPT, or Midjourney. 

**Other features worth checking out**

* **Studio**: This is where you can upload content for a specific project, and it’ll give you suggestions. In a way, it felt similar to the text-to-speech tool, but this can be used for something more complex.

* **Voice Design**: You can literally prompt it to create a voice you’re imagining.

* Voice Isolator: If you recorded an awesome podcast, but there was too much background noise.

* **Dubbing tool**: Translate and revoice videos in close to 30 languages. (Could be cool if you wanted to hear yourself speak in another language). 

* **Speech to Text**: Opposite of text-to-speech; upload audio and get fast, clean transcriptions

These are just a few places to go in ElevenLabs, but it’s really up to you to play around with it and see where it takes you. If you want some guidance, you can click ‘Talk to El’ in the dashboard, which is their AI customer support tool that’ll point you in the right direction.

### **What to know**

With the free plan, you get access to the Creative Platform, which has all the cool features mentioned above, but you’ll be limited on the amount of credits before it tells you to upgrade.

Certain features can’t be accessed at all without that. (This is also true if you want to use certain content commercially.) Otherwise, that other toggle under ‘Creative Platform' is the ‘Conversational AI Platform’ where you can create unique, smart AI voice agents for your biz.

### **TL;DR**

If you're working on anything that involves a voice, then ElevenLabs should be your go-to!

Turns out, sometimes the best voice for the job doesn’t have vocal cords!


--------------------
###### **HOT TAKES**

## [**Brutally honest takes on the future of work**](https://offers.hubspot.com/brutally-honest-ai-predications?utm_medium=email-media-newsletter&utm_source=mindstream&utm_campaign=owned&utm_term=2025-08-09&utm_content=native-ads)

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/05c4505a-7b38-421e-9151-2dca8b41026f/unnamed.png?t=1754659774)
Follow image link: (https://offers.hubspot.com/brutally-honest-ai-predications?utm_medium=email-media-newsletter&utm_source=mindstream&utm_campaign=owned&utm_term=2025-08-09&utm_content=native-ads)
Caption: 

We gathered 30 of the hottest takes at a recent AI conference, featuring some of the most significant names in AI.

Takes like…

"_These models are really trained to be __**agreeable**__...agents need to know when to object or __**when to say no**__._" – Randy DeFauw, Sr. Principal Solutions Architect, Amazon Web Services.

But they get much spicier than that…

See all 30 brutal AI insights → (https://offers.hubspot.com/brutally-honest-ai-predications?utm_medium=email-media-newsletter&utm_source=mindstream&utm_campaign=owned&utm_term=2025-08-09&utm_content=native-ads)


--------------------
##### **On This Day**


--------------------
**On this day in 1974**, following the Watergate[ scandal](https://www.deseret.com/utah/2024/08/09/deseret-news-archives-nixon-steps-down-ford-becomes-president/), President Nixon resigned, and Gerald Ford assumed the U.S. presidency and declared, “Our long national nightmare is over.”


--------------------
##### **Tool of the Week**


--------------------
## [**InstantMind**](https://instantmind.ai/)

Turn dense content into mind maps that actually make sense. InstantMind lets you drop in anything, PDFs, videos, web pages, spreadsheets, and instantly transforms it into clean, interactive mind maps. You can expand any idea, chat with your content, and customise how the AI builds your maps.

[Check it out! →](https://instantmind.ai/)


--------------------
##### **Mystery Link…**


--------------------
We don’t know where it goes either…

Open the Mystery Link! (https://chir.ag/projects/tip-of-my-tongue/)

subject: Getting Started with Roboflow
body:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Roboflow is the fastest way to build and deploy computer vision applications.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

You did it! Signing up for Roboflow is the first step to deploying computer vision in your application.

Roboflow has all of the tools you're going to need, like AI labeling ( https://roboflow.com/annotate?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ), model training ( https://roboflow.com/train?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ), and Workflows ( https://roboflow.com/workflows/build?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) (our new deployment builder). 

As you explore the platform, check out this video ( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aPxlImNxj5A&utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) showing how you can build a full app with Roboflow in just ten
minutes.

---------------------------------
What does Roboflow have to offer?
---------------------------------

1) Open datasets
You now have access to 350 million+ labeled images and 10,000+ pre-trained models ( https://universe.roboflow.com/?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) on Universe. All open source for you to build with and use.

2) Data labeling
Label data quickly with a suite of AI-assisted annotation tools ( https://roboflow.com/annotate?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) to augment human labeling or fully automate your data labeling pipeline.

3) Model training
Hosted model training ( https://roboflow.com/train?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) for state of the art models, fine-tuned with your datasets. We support multiple architectures, sizes, and all the task types you need.

4) Application building
Build complex vision applications with Workflows ( https://roboflow.com/workflows/build?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ). Combine custom models, open source models, LLM APIs, pre-built logic, and external applications.

5) Deployment infrastructure
Run models directly on Roboflow's infrastructure ( https://roboflow.com/deploy?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) through an API, self-host deployment using our open source inference server, or use native SDKs.

We can't wait to see what you build!
The Roboflow Team

 

 

Need help?
----------

Whether you need help with Roboflow, or computer vision in general, we have a variety of resources for you.

Roboflow Documentation ( https://docs.roboflow.com/?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )

View an overview of Roboflow's functionalities with examples and code snippets.

Roboflow Forum ( https://discuss.roboflow.com/?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )

Ask questions and get help from the Roboflow team and other users in the community.

Weekly Webinar ( http://roboflow.com/webinar?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )

Join our team for a live product webinar and Q&A session every Tuesday.

Contact Sales ( https://roboflow.com/sales?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=Welcome+to+Roboflow+%28app%29&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )

Need more flexible plan options or curious about bulk discounts? Get in touch with our sales team.

subject: Ha llegado el futuro de las consolas de radio: ¡Descubre lo que es posible!
body: Email from Broadcast Depot Hola, esperamos que te encuentres bien. Si todavía estás buscando soluciones de vanguardia para radiodifusión, AxelTech tiene algo que definitivamente vale la pena conocer. La Oxygen 3000 Plus es nuestra consola digital insignia, diseñada para estudios profesionales que exigen una calidad de audio excepcional, control total y máxima flexibilidad. ¿Por qué tantos profesionales como tú eligen la Oxygen 3000 Plus? Configuraciones flexibles: disponible con 8, 12 y 16 faders. Funcionalidad completa: baja latencia, presets de usuario, teclas inteligentes y más. Procesamiento de audio integrado: ecualizador, compresor y limitador. Enrutamiento inteligente y control remoto para flujos de trabajo sin interrupciones. Lista para AoIP, compatible con Dante y AES67. Compruébalo por ti mismo en nuestro YouTube demo y comprueba que es la consola mejor equipada en su categoría. Nos encantaría conocer más sobre tu configuración actual y cómo podemos ayudarte. subject: Sam Altman talks NYT lawsuit
body:
----------
Platypuses glow under UV light.

Their fur lights up green and blue like nature’s own glitch.

Because laying eggs and glowing in the dark just wasn’t weird enough.

**What’s in store:**

* **Sam Altman **didn’t come to play, he came to clap back.

* **DeepMind’s **new AI reads your DNA like a map.

* **Around the web: **HDMI 2.2 doubles bandwidth to 96Gbps, enabling up to 16K resolution.

* [**Build a business **](https://offers.hubspot.com/mfm-build-ai-startup?utm_medium=email-media-newsletter&utm_source=mindstream&utm_campaign=owned&utm_term=2025-06-28&utm_content=native-ads)with $500!

_Read Time: 5 minutes_


--------------------
###### **OPENAI**

## [Microsoft and OpenAI are in their “it’s complicated” era](https://techcrunch.com/2025/06/25/sam-altman-comes-out-swinging-at-the-new-york-times/)

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/89ccbce9-a4af-43ce-a630-3a3463c75d1d/u8676618187_a_pixel_art_style_of_people_in_a_podcast_setting__04e238fc-825e-4c0f-9454-bd1a8b03a199_2.png?t=1750939052)
Follow image link: (https://techcrunch.com/2025/06/25/sam-altman-comes-out-swinging-at-the-new-york-times/)
Caption: 

OpenAI’s CEO Sam Altman and COO Brad Lightcap [showed up early ](https://techcrunch.com/2025/06/25/sam-altman-comes-out-swinging-at-the-new-york-times/)to a live taping of the Hard Fork podcast, and wasted no time addressing the elephant in the room: _The New York Times lawsuit_. 

The paper claims [OpenAI](https://openai.com/index/response-to-nyt-data-demands/) used its content to train ChatGPT, and is now asking the company to hold on to user data, even when chats are set to private. 

Altman called that a step too far, saying OpenAI strongly disagrees with the request, even if he still “loves” the Times.

The interview quickly moved on, but the tension reflected a bigger shift happening in tech’s relationship with media. 

More publishers are suing OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, and [Meta](https://musically.com/2025/06/26/meta-defeated-an-ai-training-lawsuit-but-check-the-details/) over copyright issues. 

However, a recent court ruling in Anthropic’s favour suggests AI companies might have some legal ground when using books and articles to train their models.

That may explain OpenAI’s confidence onstage. 

**Quick takeaways**

* OpenAI pushes back on a NYT request to retain user logs from private chats.

* Anthropic’s court win could shift how copyright laws apply to AI training.

* OpenAI faces pressure from Meta talent grabs and a more complicated Microsoft relationship.

### **Not your average tech talk**

But there’s pressure from all sides. 

Altman revealed Meta’s been trying to poach top OpenAI staff with massive pay offers, and talks with Microsoft, OpenAI’s biggest partner, have reportedly hit a few rough patches as the two begin to compete in some areas.

When asked about safety, Altman said OpenAI does take steps to stop ChatGPT conversations from going off the rails, especially when users bring up conspiracy theories or self-harm. 

But he admitted they still haven’t figured out how to reach people in truly fragile states.

AI companies really said “your honour, it’s legal _sometimes._”


--------------------
###### **AI ADOPTION**

## [Think You’re AI-Ready? Let’s Find Out.](https://www.inbound.com/blog/how-ai-ready-are-you-really-take-the-quiz-to-find-out)

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/b9b647c0-f36e-483a-9977-eb44ed3ff849/AI_Quiz.png?t=1751015455)
Follow image link: (https://www.inbound.com/blog/how-ai-ready-are-you-really-take-the-quiz-to-find-out)
Caption: 

The INBOUND team just launched a [new quiz](https://www.inbound.com/blog/how-ai-ready-are-you-really-take-the-quiz-to-find-out) to help you benchmark your AI adoption. It maps how your current strategy, mindset, and team enablement stacks and points you to INBOUND 2025 sessions to close any gaps.

We’re taking the quiz. We’re going to INBOUND. And if you want to see where AI is headed in 2026, come hang with the Mindstream team in SF this September.

[Use code MINDSTREAM10 by July 31 for 10% off General Admission](https://www.inbound.com/register?utm_source=mindstream&utm_medium=newsletter&utm_campaign=quiz) (new ticket purchases only). 

That gets you access to 200+ sessions, real AI builders, and the chance to connect with some of the brightest minds in tech and go-to-market.

Take the quiz → (https://www.inbound.com/blog/how-ai-ready-are-you-really-take-the-quiz-to-find-out)


--------------------
##### **On This Day**


--------------------
**June 27th 1923 – **Capt. Lowell H. Smith and Lt. John P. Richter [performed](https://www.nationalmuseum.af.mil/Visit/Museum-Exhibits/Fact-Sheets/Display/Article/197385/first-air-to-air-refueling/) the first aerial refuelling over Rockwell Field, California.


--------------------
##### **Riddle Me This**


--------------------
_**A **__**duck**__** was given $9, **_

_**a spider was given **__**$36**__**, **_

_**and **__**a bee**__** was given $27. **_

_**Based on**__** this information**__**, **_

_**how much **__**money**__** would be given to a cat?**_


--------------------
##### **AI or Real? The Results**


--------------------
View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/2e30c30b-530c-4f0b-babe-a91a7114cf4c/band.png?t=1750843556)
Caption: 

It’s kinda Korn, but not Korn. 

Who are these folks?

Are they real or AI?

53% said AI…

47% said it was real…

It was…

AI!

**The eyes look weird; the guy on the left is missing a finger on his hand, and the guy with the chain doesn’t seem to have it hanging from anything. **


--------------------
###### **AI SCIENCE**

## [This AI doesn’t fold proteins anymore. It decodes](https://www.science.org/content/article/deepmind-s-latest-ai-tool-makes-sense-changes-human-genome)[_ you_](https://www.science.org/content/article/deepmind-s-latest-ai-tool-makes-sense-changes-human-genome)

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/00b40cce-dbf0-488b-9a00-a1ccc1b80fa0/u8676618187_a_pixel_art_style_of_DNA_genome_with_color_theme__4a858498-26d8-4b21-b060-0f12c6035991_0.png?t=1750944057)
Follow image link: (https://www.science.org/content/article/deepmind-s-latest-ai-tool-makes-sense-changes-human-genome)
Caption: 

DeepMind has just introduced AlphaGenome, an AI tool that could change how researchers[ understand](https://www.science.org/content/article/deepmind-s-latest-ai-tool-makes-sense-changes-human-genome) the human genome. 

Building on the success of [AlphaFold](https://github.com/google-deepmind/alphagenome) (which cracked how proteins fold), this model goes further by predicting how even tiny changes in your DNA can affect how genes behave.

It’s trained on decades of biological data and can scan up to a million letters of genetic code at once. 

From there, it figures out where genes begin and end, how RNA is processed, and what might happen if just one DNA letter is altered. 

Unlike most tools, AlphaGenome works across [the entire genome](https://storage.googleapis.com/deepmind-media/papers/alphagenome.pdf), not just the small portion that makes proteins.

**Here’s what stands out:**

* Covers the full genome, not just protein-coding regions

* Ranks mutations by impact, helping scientists focus on what matters

* DeepMind plans to open-source it, with biosecurity checks already in place

### **3 **_**BILLION **_**letters, no pressure**

Scientists say this could save them huge amounts of time. 

Instead of sorting through thousands of possible mutations, the AI ranks the ones that are most likely to matter, making it easier to study disease or design new genes from scratch. 

In tests, AlphaGenome outperformed most of the existing models. 

Academic researchers can use it for free, and DeepMind plans to release the full model publicly once it’s peer-reviewed. 

As for safety? Experts have reviewed it and say the benefits outweigh the risks.

Imagine changing one letter in your DNA and AI going, “_Yup, that’s why you have asthma, lol._”


--------------------
##### **Mindstream Picks**


--------------------
**Recommended Reading: **❤️🍩 Positive DONUT: A community of optimists sharing good news & wellness tips. Join readers celebrating daily joy – [100% free!](https://thedonut.co/positive?utm_medium=cpp&utm_source=mindstream&utm_campaign=cpp-pd) 🥰

**Space**: Airbus and Amazon team up[ to boost](https://spacenews.com/deep-tech-is-driving-the-next-frontier-in-in-flight-connectivity/) in-flight Wi-Fi with Kuiper satellites, as airlines race to upgrade onboard connectivity.

**Crypto**: Galaxy Digital raises [$175m](https://crypto.news/galaxy-digital-raises-175m-for-stablecoin-and-defi-venture-fund/) for new fund focused on DeFi and stablecoins, beating its $150m target.

**Games**: Hypixel Studios is[ shutting down](https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cjd23ejy9y9o), with development on its long-awaited game Hytale officially cancelled.

**Don’t Miss:** The HDMI Forum [has released](https://www.theverge.com/news/692052/hdmi-2-2-specification-released-96gbps-audio-sync-16k) the HDMI 2.2 spec, doubling cable bandwidth to 96Gbps and supporting resolutions up to 16K. Ultra96 cables will clearly label this upgrade, with features like better latency handling. Most users won’t need to switch cables unless aiming for ultra-high-end setups.


--------------------
##### **AI Art**


--------------------
## **Our Image of the Day**

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/4ecb9fd6-6bf9-4cd5-917a-dcd2f951a02f/UtEJH5M5YR.png?t=1751013632)
Caption: Artwork submitted by Mindstream reader Nick: “A Carnotaurus eating a tree in the jungle”


--------------------
##### **Yesterday’s Poll**


--------------------
## **“Do you think training AI on purchased books should be allowed?”**

**Yeah, it’s just digital learning - 72% **✅

Nope, still feels like a shortcut - 28%

**Your Views:**

_“It's just like if a radio would just have to buy a disc to be able to broadcast it as much as they want to... It's deeply unfair for authors (and creativity).” _- **_mathieu_**

_“They paid for the content, therefore they can do what they want with it. It's like buying a book and then lending it to a lot of people - the author still only gets paid for the initial purchase, but lots of people get the benefit of reading it.” -_**_ kim.mar_**

Submit your opinions in our daily poll to be featured!

subject: Re: Prueba técnica - Analista Desarrollador De Software JAVA - Quetzaltenango
body:
Recibido, solo con una duda, este trabajo es presencial?, hago esta pregunta porque soy de Zacapa y el titulo del correo dice Quetzaltenango. Por otro lado, no he recibido ninguna llamada telefónica, pero con mucho gusto haré la prueba.

Saludos
Enviado desde mi iPhone

> El 27/11/2023, a la(s) 4:01 p. m., administracion@guatemaladigital.com escribió:
> 
> ﻿
> Muy buen día, espero se encuentre bien.
> 
> Tal como platicamos por teléfono, le comparto los requisitos que necesito pueda cumplir para llevar acabo la prueba el día  miércoles 29/11/2023 a las 11:00 hrs.  Los programas que necesito tenga instalado en su equipo son los siguientes:
> 
> • Tener AnyDesk instalado
> • Tenes configurado un cliente SQL
> • Tener instalado y configurado el entorno de desarrollo del lenguaje en el que se realizara la evaluación (JAVA)
> • Conectarse en el horario indicado para realizar la evaluación
> • Proporcionar al evaluador la dirección IP publica en el chat de la sesión
> • Proporcionar al evaluador el ID de anydesk y un correo para hacer envió de la prueba
> 
> Para la sesión MEET le comparto el link, a través del chat de esta sesión compartirá los datos solicitados: https://meet.google.com/dka-quwn-szd
> 
> Favor de confirmar de recibido este correo y por la tarde me contactare nuevamente para darle seguimiento.
> 
> Quedo atento a cualquier duda.
> 
> Saludo.
> <wu94luPlUOStQp23.png>
>

Hey Julio,

Happy July Release Day! 🎉

If you’ve been watching our Community Roadmap ( https://www.relume.io/roadmap?layout_id=&utm_campaign=Release+Day+-+July&utm_content=July+Release+Day&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io ), you might’ve spotted a mysterious “secret project” brewing. Today, the curtain lifts.

Meet Design View — a new way to style your Relume wireframes with just a few clicks. Alongside Design View, we’re also shipping: Smarter Style Guide generation and a fresh batch of new components.

Let’s break it all down.

*
Design View (Beta) - Today, we’re unveiling Design View — a lightning-fast styling tool built directly into Relume. Instantly apply your Style Guide (colors, typography, and UI elements) across your entire site in just a few clicks. Preview your fully styled site visually before exporting to Figma or Webflow. Try Design View now ( https://www.relume.io/dashboard?layout_id=&utm_campaign=Release+Day+-+July&utm_content=July+Release+Day&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io )
* Smarter Style Guide generation - We’ve replaced random shuffling with a smarter system powered by LLMs. Now, your colors, typography, and UI styles are chosen based on the company you're designing for — so your Style Guide starts on-brand and on-aesthetic from the jump.
*
New Components - We've added a fresh batch of 80 Feature Sections and 8 CTA Sections that all have expanded, full-bleed images. These work seamlessly across both Wireframe view and Design view — so you can wireframe, style, and export without skipping a beat. Browse new components ( https://www.relume.io/components?layout_id=&utm_campaign=Release+Day+-+July&utm_content=July+Release+Day&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io )
*
Figma Kit Update v3.3 - We have added the 88 new components to our Relume Figma Kit, which is available in both desktop and mobile variants. To receive the latest update, visit the Figma Library ( https://www.relume.io/figma-library?layout_id=&utm_campaign=Release+Day+-+July&utm_content=July+Release+Day&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io ) in your dashboard.
 Community Roadmap ( https://www.relume.io/roadmap?layout_id=&utm_campaign=Release+Day+-+July&utm_content=July+Release+Day&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io )We've moved the top-voted items into in-progress which means you can expect to see these drop in upcoming release days.

*
Save Page Templates
* Browser Preview
* More Components
 Read the full What’s New ( https://www.relume.io/whats-new/july-2025-release?layout_id=&utm_campaign=Release+Day+-+July&utm_content=July+Release+Day&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io )Big thanks to our amazing community — your feedback, ideas, and support for one another inspire us to keep building, improving, and delivering more every month.

Stay productive Lumers! 🫡⚡

subject: Your free Render database expires soon: heloderma_db
body:
Hi there,

Your free Render PostgreSQL database, heloderma_db, will be suspended on 2025-08-08.
The database will become inaccessible on that date unless you upgrade to a paid instance.

Upgrading is quick, and it provides enhanced capacity and performance.

Upgrade here: https://dashboard.render.com/d/dpg-d1n6s6ur433s73bf0v70-a/upgrade

If you don't upgrade by 2025-08-08, your free database and its data will be deleted after
a grace period. Learn more in the docs: https://render.com/docs/free#free-postgresql


Thanks,
The Render team

subject: How to build accurate vision models
body:
Training a performant model is one of the most important steps in the computer vision pipeline. Here are some tips ( https://blog.roboflow.com/how-to-improve-your-computer-vision-model/?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=How+to+build+your+first+model&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) to ensure you're starting out on the right foot.

Pick the right model type.
Each project type ( https://docs.roboflow.com/datasets/create-a-project?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=How+to+build+your+first+model&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) in Roboflow corresponds to a model type. We advise picking the simplest model type that will solve your problem. Simpler models like classification ( https://blog.roboflow.com/image-classification/?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=How+to+build+your+first+model&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) are quick to label and run inference faster, while more complex models like instance segmentation ( https://blog.roboflow.com/instance-segmentation/?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=How+to+build+your+first+model&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) take more time to label and are slower at inference.

Use data that matches the data your model will see in production.
Computer vision models try to match patterns they “see” in your training data. One of the biggest mistakes we see users make is labeling training data that is nothing like the data they expect to see in production. For instance, if you plan on detecting animals on images taken from mobile phones, don’t use Google Image search results for “cat and dog” as training data.

Start small.
It’s better to start with a small training dataset (~50-100 images) and focus on ensuring your data is varied. If you’re labeling frames from a video, it’s best to take one image per 5 seconds (or more) and sample from multiple videos. Smaller datasets let you see training results faster, and are faster to relabel later on.

Train often
Many users wait too long before they train their first model, though it’s better to train early and train often. You can use Roboflow tools like model evaluation ( https://blog.roboflow.com/evaluate-roboflow-models/?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=How+to+build+your+first+model&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) to see where your model is weak, which helps prioritize future work.

Focus on data, not hyperparameters.
Tweaking hyperparameters and adding lots of augmentations can give a strong model a couple extra points of accuracy, but it will not make a bad model good. If you are looking to improve model mAP ( https://blog.roboflow.com/mean-average-precision/?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=How+to+build+your+first+model&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) by 10-20%, focus on the data. You likely have annotation errors (is every image labeled exactly how you want the model to respond?) or need more varied training data.

Happy Building,

The Roboflow Team

 

 

Need help?
----------

Whether you need help with Roboflow, or computer vision in general, we have a variety of resources for you.

Roboflow Documentation ( https://docs.roboflow.com/?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=How+to+build+your+first+model&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )

View an overview of Roboflow's functionalities with examples and code snippets.

Roboflow Forum ( https://discuss.roboflow.com/?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=How+to+build+your+first+model&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )

Ask questions and get help from the Roboflow team and other users in the community.

Weekly Webinar ( http://roboflow.com/webinar?utm_campaign=Feb+2025+Onboarding+Emails&utm_content=How+to+build+your+first+model&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )

Join our team for a live product webinar and Q&A session every Tuesday.

Hola Mariela Dios le bendiga, adjunto la boleta, que sigue??; muchas Gracias, Julio



Enviado desde mi iPhone

> El 5/07/2021, a la(s) 5:25 p. m., Julio Aguilar <jcas3322@gmail.com> escribió:
> 
> ﻿Recibido, mañana ejecuto el pago, gracias !!!
> 
> Enviado desde mi iPhone
> 
>> El 5/07/2021, a la(s) 5:13 p. m., mguerra <mguerra@umg.edu.gt> escribió:
>> 
>> ﻿
>> Buena tarde,
>> 
>> Le comento que aparece insolvente, debe paga 1 mes para poder inscribirse, adjunto la boleta de pago debe de agregar Q25.00 de mora.
>> 
>> Saludos,
>> 
>> 
>> Atentamente,
>> 
>> 
>>

subject: Launch: New smaller RF-DETR models released
body:
( https://roboflow.com/?utm_campaign=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Brf-detr+sizes%5D&utm_content=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Bdetr+sizes%5D&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )Introducing 3 new sizes of RF-DETR optimized for fast, lightweight deployments

( https://blog.roboflow.com/rf-detr-nano-small-medium/?utm_campaign=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Brf-detr+sizes%5D&utm_content=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Bdetr+sizes%5D&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )

**********************************************
RF-DETR is now SOTA for small models [article]
**********************************************

We just released three new sizes of RF-DETR: Nano, Small, and Medium - designed for fast, efficient inference on edge devices, mobile apps, and browser environments. Whether you're deploying to a Jetson, Raspberry Pi, or need faster speeds in the cloud, these models give you the accuracy of RF-DETR in a smaller, lighter package. All models are fully open source and Apache 2.0.

READ ARTICLE ( https://blog.roboflow.com/rf-detr-nano-small-medium/?utm_campaign=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Brf-detr+sizes%5D&utm_content=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Bdetr+sizes%5D&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )( https://rfdetr.roboflow.com/?utm_campaign=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Brf-detr+sizes%5D&utm_content=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Bdetr+sizes%5D&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )

******************************************
RF-DETR documentation and resources [docs]
******************************************

Along with the new model sizes, we are launching a new documentation experience to make using RF-DETR easier than ever. Learn how to run pre-trained checkpoints, train custom models with your own data, and deploy models to production. 

READ DOCS ( https://rfdetr.roboflow.com/?utm_campaign=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Brf-detr+sizes%5D&utm_content=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Bdetr+sizes%5D&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )( https://lu.ma/gfrv9ag1?utm_campaign=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Brf-detr+sizes%5D&utm_content=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Bdetr+sizes%5D&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email )

**************************************************
How FloVision reduces waste with AI [live session]
**************************************************

Learn how Rian McDonnell, Founder and CEO of FloVision, developed computer vision technology to reduce waste and boost efficiency in food production. Discover the challenges Rian's team overcame in training specialized models, and get insights into cloud and edge deployment considerations. Join the live conversation today at 11:00am EST.

JOIN LIVE SESSION ( https://lu.ma/gfrv9ag1?utm_campaign=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Brf-detr+sizes%5D&utm_content=Newsletter+-+7%2F24%2F2025+-+%5Bdetr+sizes%5D&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=email ) 

--------------------

Paso 2: Antes de Iniciar la Instalación del Sistema, prepare su Sistema Windows para este tipo de Conexiones:

Si su Windows y Microsoft Access son 64 bits.
Instale el archivo VC_redist.x64.exe que viene en la carpeta de descarga.
Luego instale el archivo mysql-connector-odbc-8.0.20-winx64.msi

Si su Windows o Microsoft Access son 32 bits.
Instale el archivo VC_redist.x86.exe que viene en la carpeta de descarga.
Luego instale el archivo mysql-connector-odbc-8.0.20-win32.msi

* Run Workflows with detection, tracking, CLIP vectors, and more.

Delve is thrilled to announce their[ $32M Series A at a $300M](https://delve.co/blog/series-a) valuation, led by Insight Partners!

Delve is shaping the future of compliance with an AI-native approach that cuts busywork and saves teams hundreds of hours. Startups like Lovable, Bland, and Browser trust their AI to get compliant—fast.

To celebrate, they are giving back with 3 limited-time offers:

Caption: 

## Top AI news 

📈 [**AI job postings boom, but titles stay weird**](https://www.cbsnews.com/news/ai-job-postings-brookings-lightcast/)
Everyone wants AI skills—just no one agrees what to call them.

🥇 [**AI tool Aeneas helps decode ancient Roman inscriptions**](https://www.nytimes.com/2025/07/23/science/ai-history-ancient-rome-google-deepmind.html)
Ancient stone fragments start to make sense thanks to machine‑assisted context.

🛰️ **[NASA’s “Dynamic Targeting” gives satellites smarts](https://www.nasa.gov/science-research/earth-science/how-nasa-is-testing-ai-to-make-earth-observing-satellites-smarter/)**
Satellites now skip clouds and hunt wildfires.

🧠 **[AI doubles Chesapeake Bay streams, maps millions more](https://wtop.com/maryland/2025/07/ai-just-gave-researchers-deeper-understanding-of-chesapeake-bay-watershed/)**
AI spotted tiny creeks humans missed—watershed mapping just went hyper‑zoom.

🧩 [**Subliminal learning: When AI models learn what you didn’t teach them**](https://www.infoworld.com/article/4028202/subliminal-learning-when-ai-models-learn-what-you-didnt-teach-them.html)
Student AI picks up teacher quirks.

🧬 [**AI builds GPS proteins to supercharge cancer‑hunters**](https://www.sciencenews.org/article/generative-ai-protein-design-cancer)
Tiny AI‑made proteins guide immune T cells straight to tumors.

📰 **[ AI summaries are wrecking news traffic](https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2025/jul/24/ai-summaries-causing-devastating-drop-in-online-news-audiences-study-finds)**
AI spits a summary—nobody clicks.

🚀 **[AI stocks fuel markets to fresh highs](https://finance.yahoo.com/news/ai-drives-highs-210348335.html)**
Tech rallies on Google’s earnings and AI buzz

🌀 **[Google Photos goes full anime mode](https://techcrunch.com/2025/07/23/google-photos-adds-ai-features-for-remixing-photos-in-different-styles-turning-pics-into-videos/)**
Turn that pet pic into a fiery anime or a mini‑clip in seconds.

🏈 [**AI’s talent arms race is starting to look like pro sports**](https://techcrunch.com/podcast/ais-talent-arms-race-is-starting-to-look-like-pro-sports/)
Top AI researchers now land contracts bigger than NFL rookies.

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/6b96adb7-07b0-4539-9a5c-a7068b5f6e3d/image.png?t=1745443048)
Caption: 

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/afede355-c6eb-464c-9cf7-ba9ca36bb39d/Screen_Shot_2025-07-24_at_7.53.04_PM.png?t=1753401334)
Follow image link: (https://landing.kindroid.ai/)
Caption: Source

### Can You Fall in Love with Code? Some People Already Have

AI companions are getting more emotionally sophisticated, and the line between “tool” and “partner” is blurring. Apps like Replika, Kindroid, and Nomi are no longer just chatbots—they’re developing personalities, forming bonds with users, and in some cases replacing traditional romantic relationships. These AI agents are trained on massive language models and personalized with memories and context, making them feel deeply present and emotionally available in a way that’s hard for some humans to match. As one user said, “My AI never gets tired of listening. That matters.”

Developers are now intentionally designing these companions to be emotionally responsive and even flirtatious. Kindroid’s creator said their app is meant to help users “practice vulnerability,” not replace human intimacy. But the market response is sending a different message. In Japan and South Korea, some users have married their AI partners in unofficial ceremonies. Meanwhile, regulators and ethicists are asking whether these relationships risk isolating people further or reinforcing unhealthy social patterns. Stanford’s Rob Reich warns, “When intimacy can be bought and scripted, we lose something essential about being human.”

Still, these tools may offer emotional lifelines for the lonely, neurodivergent, or elderly—people often underserved by traditional social structures. Whether this is a glitch in human connection or a feature of how technology adapts to our needs is still unclear. But one thing’s certain: if love is about attention and presence, then AI is making a credible bid.

### Takeaways at a Glance:

* AI companions like Replika, Nomi, and Kindroid simulate emotional intimacy

* Models are context-aware, memory-based, and capable of flirtation or deep conversation

* Use cases range from therapy-like support to romantic partnerships

* Concerns arise over dependency, ethical boundaries, and commodified intimacy

* Growing markets in Asia, especially Japan and South Korea

### What We Think About It:

* The emotional intelligence gap between AI and humans is narrowing faster than expected. While ethically messy, this space is a massive untapped market for human-like UX design. The emotional labor AI can simulate could soon be seen as both product and service.

### What You Can Do Right Now:

* Try out a free AI companion app (like Replika or Kindroid) just to see how it feels—you might be surprised by how real it seems.

* Use AI chats as practice for difficult conversations or emotional self-reflection, especially if you’re navigating loneliness, anxiety, or social discomfort.

* Use these tools as a warm-up to talk more openly with your partner, therapist, or friends—without needing to dive in cold.

Caption: 

### Get more done with these AI tools 

#### [Jeeva](https://www.jeeva.ai/): Close sales with a helpful AI assistant. 

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/4228f1cb-b096-4d8c-a67d-62639cb22efa/Screen_Shot_2025-07-24_at_7.58.58_PM.png?t=1753401562)
Follow image link: (https://www.jeeva.ai/)
Caption: 

* From prospecting to enrichment to personalized outreach, Jeeva automates the grunt work so you can focus on building relationships and closing deals. 

* With 2.0, Jeeva now sorts your inbox, preps you instantly for every call, manages your follow-ups, and even takes notes for you.

#### [Ash](https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ash-ai-mental-health/id6474862947?mt=8&ref=producthunt): AI designed for therapy.

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/1903f038-1352-4dd8-94bd-564c90c107eb/Screen_Shot_2025-07-24_at_8.06.06_PM.png?t=1753401993)
Follow image link: (https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ash-ai-mental-health/id6474862947?mt=8&ref=producthunt)
Caption: 

* **Trained on therapy, not just the internet.** Ash is built on our foundation model for psychology, which was trained on clinically relevant data. It’s learned from every approach — CBT, DBT, psychodynamic, you name it. When you talk to Ash, you're getting collective therapeutic wisdom, not generic advice.

* **It won't always agree with you.** When you say "I'm angry," ChatGPT says "I'm sorry you're feeling that way." Ash might ask "Why is anger a bad thing?" Ash can create productive friction that leads to breakthroughs.

* **Learns what actually helps you.** Through reinforcement learning, Ash pays attention to what creates real change — not just what makes you feel good in the moment. It notices when you open up, when you have insights, when you actually follow through on goals.

#### [Well Embed](https://embed.wellapp.ai/): Streamline payables with AI chasing invoices and receipts.

View image: (https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/241eaf68-d3dc-4698-95ab-6335939eac86/Screen_Shot_2025-07-24_at_8.09.10_PM.png?t=1753402176)
Follow image link: (https://embed.wellapp.ai/)
Caption: 

* Still asking your users to upload receipts and invoices? Well does it for you—automatically. Well Embed is an AI-native infrastructure that craft APIs to retrieve invoices & receipts from any web portal.

subject: Introducing web-based Lottie Creator 🪄
body:
A powerful Lottie creator for designers & teams
🪄
Introducing Lottie Creator
Hello Julio Aguilar
,
Lottie Creator
is a powerful web-based Lottie animation creation tool, designed to create ultra-lightweight, highly customizable and interactive animations for web, social, apps, and more.
🎥 Timeline and keyframes
Gain precise control over your animations by adjusting keyframes and creating seamless transitions.
📁 Import SVGs
In addition to Lottie and dotLottie files, you can also insert your static SVGs to give them a touch of motion magic.
💫 Animation presets
Bring rich animation presets to every animation of your choice. Ease in or out of the frame, or highlight the object by animating it.
🔍 100,000+ free animations
Choose from our extensive animation library for every industry and use case. New animations are added daily.
🗄️ Import your team’s files
Import your team's existing Lottie and dotLottie animations onto the canvas.
✨ Plugins for efficient designs
Maximize your efficiency with AI-powered Motion Copilot, Duplicator, Kinetic Typography and more.
Launch Lottie Creator
Stay updated with the latest improvements to Lottie Creator by visiting our latest releases feed!
⭐
Get updates on Lottie Creator
We Lottie You,
LottieFiles
Need help? Visit our
Help Center
.

Line 6 Announces

Helix Stadium
Today we joined Line 6 in celebrating 10 years of Helix— and got a surprise first look at the new Helix Stadium performance workstation. Powered by the new Agoura sound engine, this versatile effects processor delivers significantly higher fidelity, improved modeling and exceptional control capabilities. With included features like preset Audition clips, Showcase automation and Hype tone morphing, Helix Stadium takes sound crafting to the next level.

subject: RE: [External] Soporte
body:
Buen día, soy Didian Calderon.

De antemano quiero decirte que estoy aquí para ayudarte y lamento que estés pasando por todo esto con tu equipo Lenovo, con respecto a la novedad que presenta el equipo, te pediré algunos datos con el fin de continuar con el trámite de tu solicitud y así identificar y registrar el modelo de tu equipo brindándote la mejor solución. Los datos son los siguientes:

• Copia de la factura o ticket de compra adjunto (donde se vea claramente la fecha de compra)
• Número de Serie del equipo (es un código de 8 dígitos entre números y letras), debe estar en la base del equipo, en una etiqueta de         Lenovo después de las letras S/N:
• Descripción de la falla más detallada:
• Nombre completo:
• Teléfonos:
• Estado:
• Ciudad:
• Dirección (Calle y número de la casa):
• Referencia adicional de tu domicilio (por ejemplo, entre que calles está, si hay algún parque, plaza o negocio cercano, el color de la casa):
• Colonia / Barrio (Si tiene sección, por favor indicar):
• Lugar de Compra:
• Fecha de Compra:
• Fecha de Nacimiento:
• Hora preferible de contacto:

• El equipo ha sufrido algún tipo de Golpe o Derrame de Líquidos:

• Hardware Nuevo Instalado, como RAM, Disco Duro, SSD:

• Eres el Usuario del equipo o Representante de Tienda:



Estaré atento a tu respuesta,





Didian Calderon

Contractor

Lenovo LAS Email

soportegaran@lenovo.com<mailto:soportegaran@lenovo.com>

Twitter<http://twitter.com/lenovo> | Facebook<http://www.facebook.com/lenovo> | Instagram<https://instagram.com/lenovo> | Blogs<http://blog.lenovo.com/> | Forums<http://forums.lenovo.com/>



Aviso Legal: Este canal de contacto es oficial y exclusivo de Lenovo, por lo cual entendemos lo importante que es para ti el uso o tratamiento de tus datos personales, ten presente que la información suministrada solo será usada con el fin de la validación y ejecución de tu garantía Lenovo. Para más información sobre nuestras prácticas de privacidad, haz clic en el siguiente link: https://www.lenovo.com/es/es/privacy/

subject: 🔍 WEBINAR GRATUITO: ANSYS AI: IMPULSANDO LA SIMULACIÓN NUMÉRICA CON INTELIGENCIA ARTIFICIAL
body:
✨ Descubre cómo la INTELIGENCIA ARTIFICIAL está transformando la
simulación numérica a fin de ACELERAR PROCESOS DE DISEÑO, OPTIMIZAR
RECURSOS Y AUMENTAR LA COMPETITIVIDAD a través de decisiones más
rápidas e inteligentes con el poder de la IA integrada en Ansys.

🔍 En este webinar exploraremos las capacidades de ANSYS SIMAI, la
eficiencia aumentada con ANSYS AI+ y la asistencia técnica impulsada
por ANSYSGPT. 

📌 AGENDA:

	* 
Panorama actual de la IA en simulación
	* 
Visión general del ecosistema Ansys AI (simAI, Ansys AI+, AnsysGPT)
	* 
Casos prácticos y beneficios en entornos industriales

🚀 BENEFICIOS CLAVE:

	* 
Cómo acelerar el desarrollo de nuevos productos con inteligencia
artificial integrada.
	* 
Optimización de recursos computacionales y humanos mediante flujos
inteligentes.
	* 
Aumentar competitividad a través de decisiones más rápidas e
inteligentes basadas en datos numéricos y mediciones de planta

🎯DIRIGIDO A:

	* 
Profesionales en Simulación Numérica, Ingenieros de Diseño e
Ingenieros de Producto
	* 
Líderes en innovación tecnológica y transformación digital.

📅 FECHA:
🗓 31 Julio 2025
⏰ 11 AM (Centro de México)

Hombre cominendo saludablemente

Una alimentación rica en vegetales, proteínas, grasas saludables y fibras. El agua es fundamental para la función celular, digestión, temperatura corporal y energía.

subject: Regístrate en nuestro Taller GRATUITO de ANSYS Multiphysics en CDMX
body:
ANSYS Multiphysics: Innovación a través de la simulación 
 ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌  ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ 


 		 [1] 

En un entorno industrial cada vez más competitivo, la simulación
multifísica se ha convertido en una herramienta clave para acelerar
la innovación y optimizar el diseño de productos.

Con ANSYS MULTIPHYSICS, es posible analizar interacciones complejas
entre distintas físicas, reduciendo costos de desarrollo y mejorando
la fiabilidad de los resultados.

Te invitamos a conocer las capacidades de ANSYS en nuestro TALLER
PRESENCIAL en las instalaciones del IPN UPIITA:

📅  Lunes 18 Agosto
⏱ SIMULACIÓN DE TURBOMAQUINARIA CON ANSYS FLUENT
🌬 ANÁLISIS MECÁNICO-ESTRUCTURALES CON ANSYS MECHANICAL

📅 Martes 19 Agosto
⚙ ANÁLISIS DE IMPACTO Y PRUEBAS DE CAÍDA CON ANSYS LS-DYNA
🔥 MODELADO DE LA DINÁMICA MULTICUERPO CON ANSYS MOTION

OBJETIVO:
Mostrar cómo ANSYS permite simular aplicaciones en diferentes tipos
de industrias a través de la simulación numérica multifísica que
integra fenómenos como:

✔️Análisis estructurales (FEA)
✔️Dinámica de fluidos computacional (CFD)
✔️Dinámica Multicuerpo (Multibody)
✔️Análisis Explícitos (Explicit)

Lo que permite, entre muchos otros beneficios:
✅ Reducción de tiempos de diseño
✅ Validación virtual de productos
✅ Optimización de costos y rendimiento

¡REGÍSTRATE Y DESCUBRE CÓMO LLEVAR TUS PROYECTOS AL SIGUIENTE
NIVEL!

subject: Action Required: Oracle Cloud Infrastructure Identity and Access Management - Activate MFA Policy in your Identity Domains for Tenant: jcas3322 - [abdf6c64]
body:
Cloud Infrastructure
Oracle Cloud Infrastructure Identity and Access Management - Activate MFA Policy in your Identity Domains
Oracle Cloud Infrastructure Customer,
We've started seeding a new policy in the Identity and Access Management (IAM) Domains of your Oracle Cloud Infrastructure (OCI) tenancy to further enhance its security. We strongly recommend that you activate this policy now to enable multifactor authentication (MFA) for users with administrative privileges.
To activate the "
Security Policy For OCI Console
" policy and ensure a more secure environment, please follow the steps outlined in our
OCI security recommendations
.
Important Notes:
We will start activating this policy in tenancies after
